<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.5">
<l>nāṭu mūruma ṟiyavē pōynallatu ḻāyalaṅkal</l>
<l>cūṭināra ṇaṉpō miṭamellāñ cōtit tuḻikiṉṟāḷ</l>
<l>kēṭuvēṇṭu kiṉṟār palaruḷar kēcava ṉōṭivaḷai</l>
<l>pāṭukā valiṭumi ṉeṉṟeṉṟu pārtaṭu māṟiṉatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Adorned with garlands of fine tulasī,</l>
<l rend="indent">going recognized in coutryside and city,</l>
<l>She searches, wandering everywhere that Nāraṇaṉ went.</l>
<l>There are many residents who would ruin [us],</l>
<l rend="indent">being troubled, [they] say over and over,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Watch her with Keśava, keep her near!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
